  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > PowerDirector 21 Ultimate </h2>Empower yourself with professional editing tools, features, and high-end performance capabilities to take complete control of the video production process and workflow, without the steep learning curve.<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > New! AI Object Detection With Video Effects </h2>Automatically apply masks around people or objects to remove backgrounds, unwanted objects, or add effects. <h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2115630/extras/97aa8af91677fc3316f5a129c6a0896b.avif?t=1754574236\" width=540 height=314 /></span></h2></ul><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > New! AI Motion Tracking </h2>Create text and VFX that smoothly follow the motion of objects or even the camera itself. <h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2115630/extras/a30b08b98bcfc880bb9ca3fc4463027a.avif?t=1754574236\" width=540 height=314 /></span></h2></ul><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > New! GIF Maker </h2>Easily create and share viral animated GIFs. <h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2115630/extras/6b632780148a8ed24f0892cd9d18f78f.avif?t=1754574236\" width=540 height=314 /></span></h2></ul><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > New! Video Intro Designer </h2>Discover and create attention-grabbing video intros alongside our community of creatives. <h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2115630/extras/0970f5e0e5c2ab72930cd0d701573db1.avif?t=1754574236\" width=540 height=314 /></span></h2></ul><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > New! NVIDIA Broadcast Support </h2>Experience state-of-the-art AI capabilities designed to enhance audio and video quality. <h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2115630/extras/4ae75941f3ec8b71d0e139031f2229f0.avif?t=1754574236\" width=540 height=314 /></span></h2></ul><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > New! In/Out Animations </h2>Bring dynamic energy to your footage with a vast collection of animations for PiP objects. <h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2115630/extras/3b57d4b2eab8fed52cd71f153875fdcb.avif?t=1754574236\" width=540 height=314 /></span></h2></ul><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > Enhanced! AI Sky Replacement </h2>Enhance or totally replace the sky for perfect scenic shots. Select from a range of presets or import custom images. <h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2115630/extras/2a019ae22bf7aa36541db745294a5e4c.avif?t=1754574236\" width=540 height=314 /></span></h2></ul><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > Enhanced! Mask & Blend </h2>Layer, shape, and blend like never before with enhanced keyframe controls.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2115630/extras/3846f8a80092247cc32dbb8e70f30268.avif?t=1754574236\" width=540 height=314 /></span></h2></ul><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > Enhanced! Cinematic Effects </h2>Enhance your shots with particles, transitions, and other visual effects. <h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2115630/extras/1d621c45b87e5a658ab1642b11c9b90b.avif?t=1754574236\" width=540 height=314 /></span></h2></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > PowerDirector 21 Ultimate </h2>Empower yourself with professional editing tools, features, and high-end performance capabilities to take complete control of the video production process and workflow, without the steep learning curve.<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > New! AI Object Detection With Video Effects </h2>Automatically apply masks around people or objects to remove backgrounds, unwanted objects, or add effects. <h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2115630/extras/97aa8af91677fc3316f5a129c6a0896b.avif?t=1754574236\" width=540 height=314 /></span></h2></ul><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > New! AI Motion Tracking </h2>Create text and VFX that smoothly follow the motion of objects or even the camera itself. <h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2115630/extras/a30b08b98bcfc880bb9ca3fc4463027a.avif?t=1754574236\" width=540 height=314 /></span></h2></ul><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > New! GIF Maker </h2>Easily create and share viral animated GIFs. <h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2115630/extras/6b632780148a8ed24f0892cd9d18f78f.avif?t=1754574236\" width=540 height=314 /></span></h2></ul><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > New! Video Intro Designer </h2>Discover and create attention-grabbing video intros alongside our community of creatives. <h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2115630/extras/0970f5e0e5c2ab72930cd0d701573db1.avif?t=1754574236\" width=540 height=314 /></span></h2></ul><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > New! NVIDIA Br